Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想得到这女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:02:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第70话 再次苏醒的鬼蜘蛛记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想得到你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要阻碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么找上戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙为什么想要抓戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他背上有蜘蛛的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双应该是奈落的分身没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面承受风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不可能还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  未免太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好  托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后再来换药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的话就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双师父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的师父被杀害  脸被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真残忍  到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没有脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且背上有蜘蛛的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕  太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他进去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背上有蜘蛛的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落分身的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…又想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会在意我也是身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心依然\N强烈的残存在你的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  奈落那浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么时候才要放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  以后不会再逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追一个叫无双的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也算是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的新分身?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后告诉犬夜叉他们无双的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  那家伙会去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  对我做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是谁  犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识…那个家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你暂时回那边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次都说不要随便回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了这次没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很在意考试结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很感谢你让我回去啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘暂时躲着比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到弄清楚奈落的企图为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿的铠甲不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这景色怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的回去比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫无双的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道真实身分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他想要抓你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无双已经被\N犬夜叉的风之伤打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对犬夜叉而言还真是用心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然到目前为止\N已经和奈落的分身交战过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是他第一次这么小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那个地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到那个洞窟去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞窟的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞穴?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…知道这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目的到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落城…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有目标了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是胡乱走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说蠢话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在朝无双来的\N相反方向前进啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去被袭击的村子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强盗们被杀的地方也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是来打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想告诉你们无双在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不知为何一直很在意他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要来告诉我们这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道桔梗和鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起生活的洞窟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双正往那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双去了那个洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实的传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!是奈落唆使你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是否知道犬夜叉的秘…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多嘴了  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐似乎曾带着四魂碎片逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该不是绝对服从奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐没有告诉奈落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉朔日的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样她也不是同伴!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不能完全相信神乐说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是平常的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定马上就砍过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你在急躁什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是会不由自主的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到无双那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙什么跟什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真搞不懂…奈落那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告诉犬夜叉他们无双的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后监视那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是要\N监视那家伙的一举一动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道无双和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受奈落的支配吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你还没回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得\N自己也想去看看那个洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…曾经有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前鬼蜘蛛待过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…一切灾厄的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想得到那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…的确在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我想得到那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算向魔物出卖魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要得到桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能!怎么会是那家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得那家伙散发的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真让人难以致信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙为什么现在还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事  老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要找那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个拥有桔梗模样的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是野盗鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找的人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不会那么轻易被你抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥  你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住!\N谁理你!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有桔梗身影的你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来搅局啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?为什么在这?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有无双也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前当强盗时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这洞窟与桔梗度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在胡扯什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  这家伙是鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛就是向妖怪献上身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成奈落的大坏蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到严重烧伤的鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是没有脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这家伙才会抢别人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是鬼蜘蛛的心\N从奈落体内跑出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事我都想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗在那个时候死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你伤害了桔梗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是了为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让妖怪吞噬身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想得到四魂之玉\N与自由的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后带着桔梗\N从这洞穴离开而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我得到全新的身体后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从洞穴出来后\N所做的第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是撕裂了\N我不惜向妖怪出卖魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想要得到的女人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落诞生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还拥有鬼蜘蛛的意识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是大量妖怪的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些妖怪们最希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是身为巫女的姐姐的死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄到最后桔梗竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追随那半妖浑蛋之后而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉也随着\N桔梗的亡骸一起燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我监禁在深沉的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我不知沉睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经被丢到外面的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙完全都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有从奈落那边接到命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谁的命令都不听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看不顺眼的家伙就杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再烧光而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看最先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  就从你开始好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗明明已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然挑这时候觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先宰掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个就是那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别对戈薇出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来跟你打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘与枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们先避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道\N奈落为了什么放你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说你和奈落都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是桔梗的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此!无双的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有与众不同的再生能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少臭屁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子你那把怪里怪气的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就砍不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来这种对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的风穴应该能派上用场的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落在保护鬼蜘蛛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出毒虫\N就等于是封住了我的风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无双明明说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本不听奈落的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚奈落的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不想直接和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来找你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个拥有鬼蜘蛛的心的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我还残留着鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法对桔梗出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那是假造的身体也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明知道这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是身体就是无法对你出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以土块与骨头所构成的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形了  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀你不是因为害怕你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不是杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是毁了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N我还不能切断与鬼蜘蛛的因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的再生能力实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不信他每次都能再生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双那浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他根本不听奈落的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不受奈落的控制吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是奈落的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管砍几次都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有打倒这家伙的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也渐渐习惯这个身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  上面!
